Class StringMonoid

  • java.lang.Object
    • drjoliv.fjava.monoid.StringMonoid
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Monoid<String>

    public class StringMonoid
extends Object
implements Monoid<String>
    The monoid for Strings, the associative operation is string concatenation and the identity element is the empty String.

    drjoliv@gmail.com
